snippet.title: Halo Wars: Definitive Edition Trailer
snippet.description: Experience the original Halo Wars enhanced for Xbox One and Windows 10 PC.  The Halo Wars: Definitive Edition is included with Halo Wars 2: Ultimate Edition and features improved graphics, new achievements, and all of the DLC created for the landmark real-time strategy game.  Preorder the digital version of Halo Wars 2: Ultimate Edition and get early access to Halo Wars: Definitive Edition beginning December 20th, 2016.
